<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ASBC | Your Student's Best Companion</title>
    <script src="/static/htmx.min.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/index.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/navbar.css">
</head>
<body>
    {{ template "navbar" }}
    <!-- Header -->
    <header>
        <div class="container">
            <h1>ASBC</h1>
            <p>Your Student's Best Companion for Managing Coursework</p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Introduction Section -->
    <section class="intro">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Welcome to ASBC</h2>
            <p>
                Are you a student feeling overwhelmed by the sheer volume of assignments? 
                Do you often struggle to manage your time and avoid piling up tasks? 
                <strong>ASBC</strong> is here as the best solution for you.
            </p>
            <p>
                ASBC (A Student's Best Companion) is an innovative web platform specifically designed to help students 
                organize and manage their coursework effectively.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Why Choose ASBC -->
    <section class="why">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Why is ASBC the Best Choice?</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Easy to Use:</strong> An intuitive and easy-to-use interface, even for first-time users.</li>
                <li><strong>Access Anywhere:</strong> Access ASBC anytime, anywhere through any device connected to the internet.</li>
                <li><strong>Free:</strong> ASBC is free to use with essential features to manage your coursework effectively.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Call to Action -->
    <section class="cta">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Join ASBC Now!</h2>
            <p>Don’t let coursework pile up and stress you out. Experience the benefits of managing your coursework more effectively and efficiently.</p>
            <a href="/register" class="btn">Get Started</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer>
        <p>© 2025 ASBC | A Student’s Best Companion</p>
    </footer>

